<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7538> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7538" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Interlocutor in Cicero's ND (1.15), and perhaps a senator since he is grouped in a dialogue attributed to 76 with C. Aurelius Cotta (75) and C. Velleius, who is designated a senator. Perhaps one of the duo Balbi of De Or. 3.78 (RS, MS-RP 1.283-284).\n" .
